                            <h4 class="govuk-body govuk-!-font-weight-bold">T Levels available now:</h4>
                            <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-2 govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Digital and IT</p>
                            <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">
                                <li>
                                    <a target="_blank" class="govuk-link tl-fap--result-course" href="4416409743762-About-Digital-and-IT-industry-placements#digital-production">Digital Production, Design and Development</a>
                                </li>
