                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tl-fap--courses--box">
                            <h4 class="govuk-body govuk-!-font-weight-bold">T Levels starting September 2022</h4>
                            <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-2 govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Engineering and manufacturing</p>
                            <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">
                                <li>
                                    <a target="_blank" class="govuk-link tl-fap--result-course" href="4416396618770-About-Engineering-and-Manufacturing-industry-placements#engineering">Engineering, Manufacturing, Processing and Control</a>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <h4 class="govuk-body govuk-!-font-weight-bold govuk-!-margin-top-5 govuk-!-margin-bottom-2">Get in touch</h4>
                    <p class="govuk-body">
                        Telephone:
                        <strong>0800 028 0289</strong> |
                        <a target="_blank" href="https://www.derby-college.ac.uk" class="govuk-link tl-fap--result-website">Visit <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">DCG</span> website</a> | Email:
                        <a href="mailto:enquiries@derby-college.ac.uk" class="govuk-link govuk-!-margin-right-4 tl-fap--result-email">enquiries@derby-college.ac.uk</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="tl-fap--result">
